[section#saferecl.hp.holder.nonmem
    [:en] Non-member functions
    [:zh_CN] 非成员函数
]

[%@lib make_hazard_pointer]
[codeblock:declaration]
hazard_pointer make_hazard_pointer();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs a hazard pointer.
[:zh_CN] 构造一个涉险指针。

[para:returns]
[:en] A [`hazard_pointer] object that owns the newly-constructed hazard pointer.
[:zh_CN] 一个拥有新创建涉险指针的 [`hazard_pointer] 对象。

[para:throws]
[:en] May throw [`bad_alloc] if memory for the hazard pointer could not be allocated.
[:zh_CN] 当无法为涉险指针分配内存时可能抛出 [`bad_alloc]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member swap[!hazard_pointer]]
[codeblock:declaration]
void swap(hazard_pointer& a, hazard_pointer& b) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to [`a.swap(b)].
[:zh_CN] 等价于 [`a.swap(b)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib make_hazard_pointer_batch]
[codeblock:declaration]
void make_hazard_pointer_batch(span<hazard_pointer> batch);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If an exception is thrown, there are no effects.
[:zh_CN] 如果抛出了异常，则没有效果。

[:en] Otherwise, for each element [`e] of [`batch] such that [`e.empty()] is [`true],
constructs a hazard pointer and makes [`e] the owner of that hazard pointer.
[:zh_CN] 否则，对于 [`batch] 的每个使得 [`e.empty()] 为 [`true] 的元素 [`e]，
构造一个涉险指针并使 [`e] 为该涉险指针的所有者。

[para:throws]
[:en] [`bad_alloc] if memory for any of the newly-constructed hazard pointers
could not be allocated.
[:zh_CN] 如果无法为任何新构造的涉险指针分配内存，则抛出 [`bad_alloc]。
[div:end]

[%@lib clear_hazard_pointer_batch]
[codeblock:declaration]
void clear_hazard_pointer_batch(span<hazard_pointer> batch) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] For each element [`e] of [`batch], if [`e.empty()] is [`false],
destroys the hazard pointer owned by [`e] and makes [`e] empty.
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`batch] 的每个元素 [`e]，如果 [`e.empty()] 为 [`false]，
则销毁 [`e] 所拥有的涉险指针并使 [`e] 为空。
[div:end]
